Q3GiWDqoR3s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了首次公开的PV和<a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/special/12259" target="_blank" rel="noopener">特别网页</a>之外，还公开了Justice的专属部分“The Lookout”和望远镜“Panscope”等展现世界观的插图。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.uyarn8uv0een-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.uyarn8uv0een-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.uyarn8uv0een-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.uyarn8uv0een-300x153.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.uyarn8uv0een-768x392.webp 768w" width="1000" height="511" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.ihee4mogy114-jpg.webp 1500w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h2>轮廓</h2><h3>伊丽莎白·罗丝·血焰</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.jjaoo2io4z71-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.jjaoo2io4z71-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.jjaoo2io4z71-jpg.webp 600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.jjaoo2io4z71-225x300.webp 225w" width="600" height="800" /></a></p><p> 《猩红女王》为世界和人民开辟了一条道路。<br />他们不仅坚守在第一线，将身体奉献在前线，还用歌声感动着每个人的心。<br />一种能够唤起情绪的存在。由于他的自律性很强，有时会受到伤害，而且他的地域特点又很注重礼貌，所以他对周围的人往往很宽容。结果，他每天都扮演着组织者的角色，但似乎在一张好床上小睡一下就能治愈他的悲伤。<br /> [插画家] 墨菲斯托 [YouTube] <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@holoen_erbloodflame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/@holoen_erbloodflame</a><br /> [X] <a href="https://x.com/ERBloodflame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://x.com/ERBloodflame</a><br /> [首次登场日期及时间] 2024/6/22（星期六）12:00~（日本时间）</p><h3>吉吉·穆林</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.qoogvtvdaxxh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.qoogvtvdaxxh-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.qoogvtvdaxxh-jpg.webp 600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/ba545b3ca03d759a46964f308445e532-kix.qoogvtvdaxxh-225x300.webp 225w" width="600" height="800" /></a></p><p>在自由的旗帜下出生长大的自由奔放的“追踪者”，以及顽皮的小妖精。<br />虽然他擅长凭直觉追随目标，但他不擅长记住方向或做出深思熟虑的决定。我经常以“想太多让我头疼”为借口。<br />这种性格在日常生活中并没有改变，她本能地倾向于喜欢好玩和胡说八道。他们常常因为觉得好玩而惹上麻烦，让周围的人头疼。<br /> [插画家] Holoen Gigimurin [YouTube] <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@holoen_gigimurin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/@holoen_gigimurin</a>